<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="386" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,150,501]" pageId="8" pageNumber="386">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,317,403,429]" pageId="8" pageNumber="386">Remarks:</emphasis>
Adults of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Huo &amp; Du" authorityYear="2022" box="[444,700,403,429]" class="Insecta" family="Perlodidae" genus="Perlodinella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Plecoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="386" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tibetensis">
<emphasis box="[444,700,403,429]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="386">Perlodinella tibetensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occur in groups under rocks along the shoreline (
<figureCitation box="[1278,1365,403,429]" captionStart="FIGURE 22" captionStartId="13.[151,250,1915,1939]" captionTargetBox="[151,1437,994,1891]" captionTargetId="figure-355@13.[151,1437,993,1891]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 22. Perlodinella tibetensis Huo &amp; Du sp. nov. under rocks. A: male; B: macropterous female; C: males (photos provided by Wang Lu-Yu)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6810275" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6810275/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="386">Fig. 22</figureCitation>
). This species is distributed in the southwestern 
<collectingRegion box="[624,685,439,465]" country="China" name="Xizang" pageId="8" pageNumber="386">Tibet</collectingRegion>
, while 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Klapalek" authorityYear="1912" box="[768,876,439,465]" class="Insecta" family="Perlodidae" genus="Perlodinella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Plecoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="386" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kozlovi">
<emphasis box="[768,876,439,465]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="386">P. kozlovi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
only known in the junction of eastern 
<collectingRegion box="[1320,1378,439,465]" country="China" name="Xizang" pageId="8" pageNumber="386">Tibet</collectingRegion>
with 
<collectingRegion box="[151,241,475,501]" country="China" name="Sichuan" pageId="8" pageNumber="386">Sichuan</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion box="[296,386,475,501]" country="China" name="Qinghai" pageId="8" pageNumber="386">Qinghai</collectingRegion>
(
<figureCitation box="[401,486,475,501]" captionStart="FIGURE 23" captionStartId="14.[151,250,1058,1082]" captionTargetBox="[154,1433,181,1033]" captionTargetId="figure-20@14.[154,1433,181,1033]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 23. Distribution map of Perlodinella kozlovi Klapálek, 1912 and P. tibetensis Huo &amp; Du sp. nov. (map provided by www.tianditu.gov.cn)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6810277" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6810277/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="386">Fig. 23</figureCitation>
).
